<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_13" id="5v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_13_r1l12">Cuncʒen hund </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_13_r1l13"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> Als Jr vns <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>geſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt / vvie euch geſagt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_13_r1l14">ſey vvorden . daʒ vvir dyener vnd Soldner bedürffen / vnd daʒ Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_13_r1l15">vns gern dienen wolt etc . des dancken vvir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> freuntſchaft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_13_r1l16"><expan>fleiſſiklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd tun ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> cʒu vviſſen . daʒ vvir cʒu dercʒeit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_13_r1l19">niht 
<add><ab facs="#facs_13_r1l17">willen <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab></add> dyener oder Soldner 
<add><ab facs="#facs_13_line_1571223499203_472">ʒe </ab></add> <expan>ſchreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . 
<del rend="strikethrough">vvurden </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_13_r1l18">gewunnen </ab></add> vvir aber 
<del rend="strikethrough">hin </del> des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_13_r1l20">hinfür <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> . So vvölten vvir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> an euch gedenken . vnd wo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_13_r1l21">vvir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb oder <expan>freuntſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> beweıſen möhten / das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_13_r1l22">teten vvir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> . <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vj̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> vrbani Anno xix<hi rend="sup">no</hi></ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_13" id="5v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Cunczen Hund </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>, als ir uns <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt wie euch gesagt sey worden, daz wir
                        dyener und soldner bedürffen und daz ir uns gern dienen wolt etc., des
                        dancken wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> freuntschaft
                                <expan>fleissiklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und tun ewr
                                <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> czu wissen, daz wir czu derczeit
                        niht <add>willen <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan></add>, dyener oder soldner
                            <add>ze</add>
<expan>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <add>Gewunnen</add> wir aber des hinfür
                                <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>, so wölten wir
                            <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> an euch gedenken; und wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb oder
                            <expan>freunts<ex>chaft</ex></expan> beweisen möhten das teten wir
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> urbani anno
                            xix<hi rend="sup">no</hi>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
